{"title":"Apple Rolls Out New Spring Accessories Including Colorful iPhone Cases, Apple Watch Bands, and AirTags Holders","link":"https://www.macrumors.com/2021/04/20/apple-new-iphone-12-magsafe-cases/","date":1618940148000,"content":"As is typical for <a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-event/\">Apple event</a> days, there are now a wide array of new accessories available on Apple.com for <a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/guide/iphone/\">iPhone</a>, Apple Watch, <a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/ipad/\">iPad</a>, and more.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>iPhone</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nStarting with <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MK033ZM/A/iphone-12-12-pro-silicone-case-with-magsafe-amethyst?fnode=d92d9a88d564141dee72a007169729e355962e679fb6b2c8d60260b7d4fc4822465c4e250528d2e7edab26eda98dcb22de5e44b0992a62458a0658bca7f0c2ba02471553eed50e86f64b74d79ff80b5fdfe9f1f95a5bfb6ee8fa2e954f8c2336\">Silicone Cases for the iPhone 12, 12 Pro</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MK073ZM/A/iphone-12-pro-max-silicone-case-with-magsafe-cantaloupe?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">12 Pro Max</a> there are four new colors: Amethyst, Capri Blue, Cantaloupe, and Pistachio. You'll find the same new colors for <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJYV3ZM/A/iphone-12-mini-silicone-case-with-magsafe-pistachio?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">iPhone 12 mini</a>.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/iphone-12-spring-cases.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJYR3ZM/A/iphone-12-12-pro-leather-case-with-magsafe-deep-violet?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">Leather Cases for iPhone 12, 12 Pro</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MHKH3ZM/A/iphone-12-pro-max-leather-case-with-magsafe-california-poppy?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">12 Pro Max</a> include one new color: Deep Violet. <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJYQ3ZM/A/iphone-12-mini-leather-case-with-magsafe-deep-violet?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">iPhone 12 mini</a> also has this color.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/accessories-stuff.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\nThe <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MK0E3ZM/A/iphone-leather-wallet-with-magsafe-arizona?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">iPhone Leather Wallet</a> now comes in Arizona; the <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MK0D3ZM/A/iphone-12-pro-max-leather-sleeve-with-magsafe-deep-violet?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">iPhone 12 Pro Max</a> and <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MK093ZM/A/iphone-12-mini-leather-sleeve-with-magsafe-deep-violet?fnode=d2a46aa84656a9e5fa2f2fffd325db0fe3e83beac1066633d9a91eef20d2a609bd746dec1c02710b399d2184df03f09eec86d976e84bf43a01303ac5186d999694144682e14f16326175e45c115c8fbfb56920b5ae191c7be99b223e0d43f006ff89b65167e0a8068df19da4e14baabe\">12 mini Leather Sleeve</a> both now come in Deep Violet.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>iPad</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nThe major new ‌iPad‌ accessory is the <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJQL3LL/A/magic-keyboard-for-ipad-pro-129%E2%80%91inch-5th-generation-us-english?fnode=c7fbf6281dea985a6cd6df927b27103489a1cd1269276b4ef74bda052c9c29214905ce83cb9178ec6e190cd77a5b77d3c57024e347a14b765d57e43c1c7fb21a7ecc830bccee25f3445266b1df840f8a41d6d600fcb6c9caf25c2d8dc7c6ad18\">Magic Keyboard for iPad Pro</a> in White for $349.00 (12.9-inch).\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/ipad-pro.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\nOtherwise, we're seeing the usual collection of new spring colors. The <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJM53ZM/A/smart-folio-for-ipad-air-4th-generation-mallard-green?fnode=3c61fbaa6d3fb71645977b6b33bb7b43e524f80f75257b07eb694ba478c782fe06bd9ab2d75f2a43a2abb265f71e26c138183b3c257003c7ffe4015bdbe0c5be1bb4d9cc71399a271cb12fd7e1e8aec273e229d29b663b2a24fb47b4748a1362f6323cfc9f2f10ff6eaa0faf4d2cc015\">Smart Folio for iPad Air</a> is now available in Mallard Green and Electric Orange. It runs for $79.00.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\nThe <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJMA3ZM/A/smart-folio-for-ipad-pro-11-inch-3rd-generation-white?fnode=3c61fbaa6d3fb71645977b6b33bb7b43e524f80f75257b07eb694ba478c782fe06bd9ab2d75f2a43a2abb265f71e26c138183b3c257003c7ffe4015bdbe0c5be1bb4d9cc71399a271cb12fd7e1e8aec273e229d29b663b2a24fb47b4748a1362f6323cfc9f2f10ff6eaa0faf4d2cc015\">Smart Folio for 11-inch iPad Pro</a> is now available in White, Mallard Green, and Electric Orange. It runs for $79.00.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/ipad-cases.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\nSimilarly, the <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJMJ3ZM/A/smart-folio-for-ipad-pro-129-inch-5th-generation-deep-navy?fnode=3c61fbaa6d3fb71645977b6b33bb7b43e524f80f75257b07eb694ba478c782fe06bd9ab2d75f2a43a2abb265f71e26c138183b3c257003c7ffe4015bdbe0c5be1bb4d9cc71399a271cb12fd7e1e8aec273e229d29b663b2a24fb47b4748a1362f6323cfc9f2f10ff6eaa0faf4d2cc015\">Smart Folio for 12.9-inch iPad Pro</a> is now available in White, Mallard Green, and Electric Orange. It runs for $79.00.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\nThe <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJM73ZM/A/smart-cover-for-ipad-8th-generation-mallard-green?fnode=3c61fbaa6d3fb71645977b6b33bb7b43e524f80f75257b07eb694ba478c782fe06bd9ab2d75f2a43a2abb265f71e26c138183b3c257003c7ffe4015bdbe0c5be1bb4d9cc71399a271cb12fd7e1e8aec273e229d29b663b2a24fb47b4748a1362f6323cfc9f2f10ff6eaa0faf4d2cc015\">Smart Cover for iPad</a> has all of the same new colors: White, Mallard Green, and Electric Orange. It runs for $49.00.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\nLast for iPads, the <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJM63ZM/A/ipad-mini-smart-cover-electric-orange?fnode=3c61fbaa6d3fb71645977b6b33bb7b43e524f80f75257b07eb694ba478c782fe06bd9ab2d75f2a43a2abb265f71e26c138183b3c257003c7ffe4015bdbe0c5be1bb4d9cc71399a271cb12fd7e1e8aec273e229d29b663b2a24fb47b4748a1362f6323cfc9f2f10ff6eaa0faf4d2cc015\">Smart Cover for iPad mini</a> now comes in Mallard Green and Electric Orange as well. It runs for $39.00.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>AirTags</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nThere are quite a few <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/accessories/all/airtag\">new accessories for AirTags</a>. You can get a Leather Key Ring for $35, Leather Loop for $39, Loop for $29, Hermès Key Ring for $349, Hermès Luggage Tag for $449, and Hermès Bag Charm for $299. \r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/Apple_airtag-accessories-042021_big_carousel-1.jpg.large_-1.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\nThere's also a Belkin Secure Holder with Strap for $12.95, and a Belkin Secure Holder with Key Ring for $12.95.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>Apple Watch</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nOf course, Apple Watch has also gained a ton of new band colors. Starting with the <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJGP3AM/A/40mm-tomales-blue-solo-loop-size-1?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Solo Loop</a>, there's Tomales Blue, Pistachio, and Cantaloupe.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/solo-loop.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJJ63AM/A/40mm-electric-orange-braided-solo-loop-size-1?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Braided Loop</a> now has Electric Orange, Pistachio, and Pink Punch.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJK43AM/A/40mm-mallard-green-sport-band-regular?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Sport Band</a> now comes in Mallard Green, Cantaloupe, and Capri Blue.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/sport-band.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJFW3AM/A/40mm-productred-sport-loop?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Sport Loop</a> comes in Sea Salt, Sunflower, Abyss, Olive, and (Product)RED.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/sport-loops.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJ6H3AM/A/40mm-chlorine-blue-green-glow-nike-sport-band-regular?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Nike Sport Band</a> comes in Chlorine Blue/Green Glow, Hasta/Light Silver, and Ironstone/Black.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/nike-sport-loop.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\nLeather now includes a new <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJKE3AM/A/40mm-chalk-leather-link-m-l?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Chalk Leather Link</a> band.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJ5R3AM/A/apple-watch-herm%C3%A8s-44mm-kraft-rouge-de-c%C5%93ur-jumping-single-tour?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Hermès</a> has the Noir/Bleu Saphir Jumping Single Tour, Rouge de Coeur Jumping Single Tour, Kraft/Rouge de Coeur Jumping Single Tour, Orange/Rose Mexico Jumping Single Tour, and Bleu Saphir/Orange Jumping Single Tour.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2021/04/new-hermes.jpg\" />\r\n<br />\r\nLastly, there's the <a href=\"https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJ5U3AM/A/apple-watch-herm%C3%A8s-40mm-noir-swift-leather-attelage-double-tour?fnode=3ddf5b57977abb7955b5eb322091f79bbe8e11483c206d107543b06855864a01086896e19b3c47d6df855471d204dd273aef122170aea0d3288b39b1519fb063a897cae2660aa82970a5b9eeb62a54ac\">Hermès</a> Rose Mexico Swift Leather Attelage Double Tour, Bleu Saphir Swift Leather Attelage Double Tour, Blanc Swift Leather Attelage Double Tour, and Noir 